<div id="review_1260994396" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1260994396" />
    <a title="Greg" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/39346323-greg"><img alt="Greg" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1513962691p2/39346323.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1260994396?book_show_action=true">Apr 21, 2015</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Greg" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Greg" href="/user/show/39346323-greg">Greg</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1260994396" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12707438364894461946">I like to read novels set in locations around the world (to me this often serves as a good travel guide) and I can&apos;t recall if I&apos;ve read a crime novel set in Northern Ireland. Even though this was a bit too violent for me, I did enjoy it. On my next trip to Ireland, I do want to head north and visit Belfast and other areas, and I hope I don&apos;t run into any of these types of characters.</span>
  <span id="freeText12707438364894461946" style="display:none">I like to read novels set in locations around the world (to me this often serves as a good travel guide) and I can't recall if I've read a crime novel set in Northern Ireland. Even though this was a bit too violent for me, I did enjoy it. On my next trip to Ireland, I do want to head north and visit Belfast and other areas, and I hope I don't run into any of these types of characters.</span>
